PEOPLE v. CLOVER FARMS CO., Appellant (six cases). (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, First Department. May 16, 1913.)

Proceedings by the People of the State of New York against the Clover Farms Company. M. Kirtland, of New York City, for appellant. R. P. Beyer, of New York City, for the People. No opinion. Determination (133 N. Y. Supp. 421) affirmed, with costs. Orders filed.
